Champions League
PSG - Bruges: the canvas ignites for the victory of the Parisians!
Paris Saint-Germain beat Brugge on Tuesday night. Discover the reaction of Internet users, disappointed with the delivery of Parisians.
06 Nov 2019, 22:16 by Rafael Da Silva
This Tuesday night, Paris Saint-Germain received Brugge FC for the fourth group match of the Champions League. Thanks to a Mauro Icardi realization in the first half, Thomas Tuchel's men won a short header (1-0), without convincing. Despite the lackluster performance of the Parisians, qualifying in the round of 16 is won, they who won their 4 games without conceding a goal.
Discover the best reactions of the Net surfers after the victory!
